  <section id="about">
  <h2>About Us</h2>
  <p>Cal Poly Urbanists is a student-led city planning activist club dedicated to improving pedestrian and bicycle infrastructure on campus and in San Luis Obispo.</p>
  <p><strong>Mission Statement:</strong> We are looking to promote the real world application of planning principles in order to empower Cal Poly students to enact the change they wish to seek. We emphasize the importance of diversity, equity, and inclusion as inseparable from the planning process and we practice thorough community engagement through our activism.</p>
