  <section id="speakers-tours">
    <h2>Tours & Guest Speakers</h2>
    <p>Over the years, Cal Poly Urbanists has hosted a variety of engaging guest speakers and educational tours to enrich our members' understanding of urban planning. These events connect students with professionals and practitioners in the field, providing real-world insight into urban development, advocacy, and community planning. Notable highlights include walking tours of downtown San Luis Obispo led by city planners, guest talks from YIMBY organizers, and panel discussions with local transportation and housing experts.</p>
